               Finally, cell-to-cell interaction analysis indicated that the
               dermal papilla lineage is the primary source of the noncanonical
               Wnt pathway during skin development. Together, our study provides
               a transcriptomic reference for future research in the field of
               skin development and regeneration.",
  month     =  jun,
