  number    =  6,
  pages     = "1619--1632",
  abstract  = "Skin aging is an intricate biological process consisting of
               intrinsic and extrinsic alterations of epidermal and dermal
               structures. Retinoids play an important role in epidermal cell
               growth and differentiation and are beneficial to counteract skin
               aging. Cellular retinoic acid binding protein-II (CRABP-II)
